comment.text: This translation key is used for displaying process details in a UI. It's displayed as a heading in a filling status panel and related to file information.

usage.context:
<Heading
 fontSize="14px"
 className={styles.processTitle}
 level={HeadingLevel.h5}
 >
 {t("Common:ProcessDetails")}
 </Heading>
 <FillingRoleProcess
 fileStatus={fillingStatus}
 processDetails={formFillingStatus}
 currentUserId={user.id}

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation "Обработи данни" (Obraboti danni) translates to 'Processes data' or 'Data processing', not 'Process details'. It doesn't accurately convey the meaning of the English phrase.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: A more accurate translation might be "Подробности за процеса" (Podrobnosti za protsesa) which means 'Process details'.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Armenian translation 'Գործընթացի ամնրամասներ' doesn't accurately convey the meaning of 'Process details'. 'ամնրամասներ' implies 'components' or 'aspects,' which isn't a direct equivalent of 'details'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider alternatives such as 'Գործընթացի մանրամասներ' (Gorts'entaci manramasner) which directly translates to 'Process details' or 'Գործընթացի տեղեկություններ' (Gorts'entaci tegequtyuner) meaning 'Process information'.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'ප්‍රති ක්‍රියාවලියේ විස්තරాలు' (prati kriyavaliye vistharalu) is too literal and not the most natural way to say 'Process details' in Sinhala. 'ප්‍රති ක්‍රියාවලිය' (prati kriyavaliya) translates to 'counter-process' or 'reactive process,' which is not synonymous with 'Process details'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider alternatives like 'ප්‍රតិ ක්‍රියාවලියෙහි තොරතුරු' (prati kriyavaliyehi thorathuru) – which translates to 'Process information' or simply 'ප්‍රති ක්‍රියාවේ විස්තර' (prati kriyaye visthar) - 'Process description'.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation "Chi tiết về Quy trình" is technically correct, but lacks the directness and conciseness of the English "Process details." "Chi tiết về Quy trình" is a more verbose phrasing. A more direct translation might be "Chi tiết quy trình".
